{"article_id":"Q1WVxS2kZvlikaMd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump is to impose 25 % tariffs on $ 50bn worth of Chinese goods ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"accusing Beijing of intellectual copyright theft .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Tariffs","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that affect more than 800 products worth $ 34bn in annual trade","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"are due to come into effect on 6 July .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The White House said","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"it would consult on tariffs on the other $ 16bn of products ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and would apply these later .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"China retaliated ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"it will impose an additional 25 % tariff on 659 US goods worth $ 50bn .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"The US had earlier warned","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"that it will impose even more tariffs","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"should China retaliate .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the tariffs were `` essential to preventing further unfair transfers of American technology and intellectual property to China ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which will protect American jobs . ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The Chinese product lines","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that have been hit","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"range from aircraft tyres to turbines and commercial dishwashers .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"In response , China announced tariffs on $ 34bn of US goods","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"including agricultural products , cars and marine products","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"which will also take effect from 6 July .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Tariffs on other US goods will be announced at a later date ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the Xinhua news agency reported .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"`` If the US takes unilateral and protectionist measures","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that harm Chinese interests ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"we will respond immediately","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"by taking the necessary decisions","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to safeguard our legitimate rights and interests , ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Chinese foreign ministry spokesman Geng Shuang said earlier on Friday .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"All trade talks between China and the US would be void","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"if Washington imposed trade sanctions ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"he added .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Stock markets dropped in Europe and the US after the announcements","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"with investors concerned about a possible trade war .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"The US wants China to stop practices","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"that allegedly encourage transfer of intellectual property","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"- design and product ideas -","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to Chinese companies , such as requirements","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that foreign firms share ownership with local partners","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"to access the Chinese market .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"However many economists and businesses in the US say","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"the tariffs are likely to hurt some of the sectors","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"the administration is trying to protect ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"which depend on China for parts or assembly .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Economists estimate","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that the tariffs will hurt GDP by less than half of a percentage point .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"But the measures could also lead to higher prices and job losses in some industries .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"The Motor and Equipment Manufacturers Association ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"which represents car parts makers ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"called the tariffs `` taxes","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that hurt U.S. companies ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"put jobs at risk ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and negatively impact consumers . ''","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Boat-makers ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"which are also facing higher costs due to US tariffs on steel and aluminium ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"will now be hit with tariffs on almost 300 parts ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"said the National Marine Manufacturers Association .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"The organisation described the tariffs as `` bad trade policies","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that are piling up on top of each other '' .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The International Monetary Fund","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"( IMF )","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"warned","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that the dispute could hurt business and consumer confidence .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"IMF Director Christine Lagarde said Thursday","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that a trade war would lead to `` losers on both sides ''","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and could have a `` serious '' impact .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"The US announced plans for tariffs this spring , after an investigation into China 's intellectual property practices .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"It published a draft list of about 1,300 Chinese products","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"slated for tariffs in April .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"The list","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"released Friday","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"incorporates feedback and criticism","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"received in the ensuing weeks .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"It contains about 1,100 items ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"including about 285 newly proposed items","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"- such as items for the semiconductor industry -","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that are subject to further review .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"The White House said","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"the measures should n't hurt consumers ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"pointing out","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"that items such as televisions","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"that were included on the draft list","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"had been taken off the list .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"It will also allow companies to apply for exclusions from the duties .","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"The plans have elicited a mixed political reaction ,","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"drawing praise from Democrats and opposition from Republicans ,","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"who typically favour free trade policies .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Senator Chuck Schumer , a leading Democrat , said","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"the president 's actions were `` on the money ''","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"He said :","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"`` China is our real trade enemy ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"and their theft of intellectual property and their refusal","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"to let our companies compete fairly","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"threatens millions of future American jobs . ''","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Republican Kevin Brady said","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"it was `` encouraging ''","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"that the administration had revised the initial list","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"but urged the White House to further narrow the items","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"subject to the tariffs .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"He said :","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"`` My message has been consistent :","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"we need to hit our target ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"which is China and its deceptive and harmful trading practices .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"But I am concerned","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that these new tariffs will instead hurt American manufacturers , farmers , workers , and consumers . ''","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Trump talked about the forgotten people , white working-class folks , at his inauguration .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"But the plans","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"to impose tariffs","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"will hurt individuals in the farm belt , an important part of his base .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Recently , I visited Missouri ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"driving past soybean fields ,","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"and heard people talk about the way","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"China would retaliate ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"imposing tariffs on soybeans .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"White House aides have warned Trump about implications of his policies .","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"One official told me","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"they 'd haul in maps","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"to show him rural states and how they 'd be affected .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Later , though , he 'd move ahead with tariffs and other policies","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"that were upsetting for Missourians and those in the farm belt .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":189,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":146,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":132,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":126,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":123,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":5,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":8,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":134,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":11,"right":133